name: CatTranslator
0:
”Alexa, start cat translator and tell my cat lets play”
”Alexa, start cat translator and tell my cat go away”
”Alexa, start cat translator and disappear”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: cat translator
des:
This skill make a easy conversation between you and your cat. Be surprised how are the reactions from your cat if Alexa speak to it. Use this skill to make a conversation with your cat. If you have only one cat at your home the skill works better.
Have fun!

Available commands:
Hello cat
let´s play
let´s cuddle
go away
purr
ultrasonic (shoos each cat close to Alexa)
Language analysis
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
